{"tid":2229994,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得內心好空虛？","createTime":"2020-10-04T17:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T17:15:49.000Z","uid":360762,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d64cf5ed37ce2a0491a67ee439b725df954bb3f7","tid":2229994,"uid":360762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T17:09:44.000Z","msg":"明明生活得好好地⋯<br />\n但係近年，<br />\n思考自己前途，<br />\n朋友要移民就移民，<br />\n生活壓力又大，<br />\n總覺得自己好無用好廢。<br />\n<br />\n但無啦啦同人講我好空虛，<br />\n佢哋應該以為我痴左線。<br />\n「明明你生活已經好好，<br />\n仲有咩值得唔開心。」<br />\n<br />\n個個都以為我好識social ，好樂觀果種。<br />\n但其實一入夜 訓教前，<br />\n就會想東想西，<br />\n一個人想很久。<br />\n然後隔天早上又回復正常，<br />\n重複又重複的生活，<br />\n重複的節奏和心情起伏。<br />\n<br />\n(純發洩文)"},{"pid":"ae4e640f4a3cdb60da9478677a2223ffc005410d","tid":2229994,"uid":333547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T17:10:54.000Z","msg":"我明"},{"pid":"54c16e7e92724075a52b3399312e227246d86177","tid":2229994,"uid":94824,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T17:12:20.000Z","msg":"以為自己開post"},{"pid":"3fe35d81471a8897126459bc124836fc161a44ef","tid":2229994,"uid":333547,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T17:13:44.000Z","msg":"有時唔好怕講出嚟  當然唔好講畀啲八婆大喇叭聽周街唱<br />\n不過情緒唔會無啦啦消失  只會越積越多"},{"pid":"8849fe7179003852af49aad2826e330f54bb228c","tid":2229994,"uid":345195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T17:17:15.000Z","msg":"覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要喺香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真唔好成日屌人移民撚移民撚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你喺香港環境咁壓抑競爭咁大<br />\n連物質滿足都未做到，點講到內心呢？<br />\n唯有自己行多啲山睇多啲書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca42c6cf5e2566ea1d09565aedd2bfd7d0d61fd6","tid":2229994,"uid":360762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8849fe7179003852af49aad28